  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 11445440864443
    m_Localized: Independence Day is on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864442
    m_Localized: "Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie was a scientist."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864441
    m_Localized: The Polish flag is white and red.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864440
    m_Localized: Parliament is where laws are made.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864439
    m_Localized: King Sigismund moved the capital to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864438
    m_Localized: Chopin was a famous Polish composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864437
    m_Localized: The Mermaid is a symbol of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864436
    m_Localized: "The Wis\u0142a River flows through Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714496
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864434
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid and reassemble the sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864433
    m_Localized: The seventh sword piece is yours! You have all 7 pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864432
    m_Localized: "Mazurek D\u0105browskiego is Poland's national anthem."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864431
    m_Localized: The soccer field is the place where the match is played.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864430
    m_Localized: The goal is where players try to score.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864429
    m_Localized: The ball is what players kick across the field.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864428
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports played here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714497
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714498
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714499
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714500
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714501
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864422
    m_Localized: "The Mazurek D\u0105browskiego is Poland's national anthem."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714502
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864420
    m_Localized: Lewandowski has scored many goals for Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714503
    m_Localized: They will tell you how people travel around the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864418
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714504
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864416
    m_Localized: The National Stadium opened in 2012.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864415
    m_Localized: He has scored many goals for his teams and for Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864414
    m_Localized: Robert Lewandowski is one of Poland's most famous footballers.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864413
    m_Localized: It opened in 2012 and hosted big football matches.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864412
    m_Localized: "The National Stadium stands on the right bank of the Wis\u0142a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864411
    m_Localized: Talk to the blue people around the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864410
    m_Localized: I am Robert Lewandowski. Welcome to the National Stadium!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864409
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864408
    m_Localized: Great work at the stadium! Return to the Mermaid with all the pieces.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864407
    m_Localized: We are at the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864406
    m_Localized: Cross the river and go to the National Stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714505
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714506
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864403
    m_Localized: "Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie was a great Polish scientist."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714507
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714508
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714509
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714510
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714511
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864397
    m_Localized: "The z\u0142oty is the money used in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714512
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864395
    m_Localized: She was the first woman to win a Nobel Prize.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714513
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864393
    m_Localized: "Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie was born in Warsaw in 1867."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864392
    m_Localized: She was the first woman to win a Nobel Prize, and she won two.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864391
    m_Localized: "Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie was a Polish scientist."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864390
    m_Localized: It was built in the 1950s and has a great view from the top.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864389
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is the tallest building in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714514
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864387
    m_Localized: Talk to the purple people around the Palace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864386
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864385
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. The chest is open. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864384
    m_Localized: We are at the Culture Palace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864383
    m_Localized: Now go to the Palace of Culture and Science.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864382
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714515
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864380
    m_Localized: Chopin was a Polish composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714516
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714517
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714518
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714519
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714520
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864374
    m_Localized: "This monument stands in \u0141azienki Park in Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714521
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864372
    m_Localized: There are free concerts here every Sunday in summer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714522
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864370
    m_Localized: He wrote famous music.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714523
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864368
    m_Localized: Chopin was born near Warsaw in 1810.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864367
    m_Localized: "This monument stands in \u0141azienki Park in Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864366
    m_Localized: He is one of the most famous composers in the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864365
    m_Localized: Fryderyk Chopin was born near Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864364
    m_Localized: Talk to the green people around and learn about Chopin.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864363
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864362
    m_Localized: The melody is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864361
    m_Localized: Parliament still needs your help. Go there first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864360
    m_Localized: We are at Chopin Park.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864359
    m_Localized: Continue to the Chopin Monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714524
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714525
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864356
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714526
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714527
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714528
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714529
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714530
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864350
    m_Localized: Independence Day in Poland is on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714531
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864348
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714532
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864346
    m_Localized: The Sejm is where people make laws in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242244714533
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864344
    m_Localized: The Polish flag is white on top and red below.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864343
    m_Localized: It is where the President of Poland works.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864342
    m_Localized: "The Presidential Palace is nearby on Krakowskie Przedmie\u015Bcie."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864341
    m_Localized: It meets in Warsaw and makes laws for Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864340
    m_Localized: The Polish parliament is called the Sejm and the Senate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864339
    m_Localized: Talk to the red and yellow people to learn about our flag and laws.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864338
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Polish Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864337
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864336
    m_Localized: The flag is sorted. Keep going and find the rest of the sword!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864335
    m_Localized: We are in front of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864334
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908800
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908801
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908802
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908803
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908804
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908805
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908806
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864326
    m_Localized: Today, Parliament makes the laws for Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908807
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864324
    m_Localized: The Royal Castle is right next to the column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908808
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864322
    m_Localized: This column has stood in the square for a very long time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908809
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864320
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund moved the capital from Krak\xF3w to Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864319
    m_Localized: It was destroyed in World War II and rebuilt later.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864318
    m_Localized: The Royal Castle stands right next to the column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864317
    m_Localized: His column in Castle Square is one of the oldest monuments in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864316
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864315
    m_Localized: Talk to the yellow people in the square and learn about our history.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864314
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864313
    m_Localized: The Square is peaceful again. Keep going and find the rest of the
      sword!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864312
    m_Localized: Go to the Old Town Square and speak with King Sigismund.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908810
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908811
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908812
    m_Localized: "Learn about science and the z\u0142oty."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908813
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908814
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908815
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908816
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864304
    m_Localized: "The Wis\u0142a River flows all the way to the Baltic Sea."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908817
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864302
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908818
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864300
    m_Localized: "The Wis\u0142a River is the longest river in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864299
    m_Localized: Talk to the blue people by the river and learn about our city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864298
    m_Localized: "I am Wars. Our statue stands by the Wis\u0142a River."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864297
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864296
    m_Localized: The chest is open. Keep going!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864295
    m_Localized: "The Wis\u0142a River flows through Warsaw all the way to the Baltic
      Sea."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864294
    m_Localized: People say their names are hidden inside the name "Warszawa."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864293
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864292
    m_Localized: "Go to the Wars and Sawa statue by the Wis\u0142a River."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864291
    m_Localized: Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864290
    m_Localized: You found a piece of the sword!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864289
    m_Localized: It is locked. You need all the keys!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864288
    m_Localized: To open the chest, solve this puzzle!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864287
    m_Localized: The chest is empty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864286
    m_Localized: You found all the keys! Now go open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908819
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864284
    m_Localized: I think the bus is the best.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908820
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864282
    m_Localized: I love going by train.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908821
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864280
    m_Localized: I like bikes, so I go by bike.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908822
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864278
    m_Localized: I like going by car.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864277
    m_Localized: Here is a key for you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864276
    m_Localized: I usually go by tram.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864275
    m_Localized: She is half woman, half fish, and carries a sword and a shield.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864274
    m_Localized: The Mermaid of Warsaw is called the Syrenka.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864273
    m_Localized: And get all the keys to open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14242248908823
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864271
    m_Localized: Talk to all the red people.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864270
    m_Localized: Antura broke the sword into 7 pieces and locked each one in a chest
      across Warsaw!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864269
    m_Localized: Open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864268
    m_Localized: Explore Warsaw and find all the pieces of the sword!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864267
    m_Localized: Now let's see what you remember from this adventure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864266
    m_Localized: The Mermaid is a symbol of Warsaw and protects the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11445440864265
    m_Localized: You collected all the pieces of the sword! Now I can make it whole
      again!
    m_Metadata:
